<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>물품 입출고 내역</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                <i data-lucide="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">물품 입출고 내역</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">모든 물품의 입고 및 출고 기록을 확인합니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <form action="{{searchUrl}}" method="GET" class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center bg-slate-50 gap-4">
                <div class="flex gap-2 w-full md:w-auto overflow-x-auto pb-2 md:pb-0">
                    <button type="submit" name="type" value="ALL" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap {{#isTypeAll}}bg-slate-800 text-white{{/isTypeAll}}{{^isTypeAll}}bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100{{/isTypeAll}}">전체</button>
                    <button type="submit" name="type" value="INBOUND" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap {{#isTypeInbound}}bg-slate-800 text-white{{/isTypeInbound}}{{^isTypeInbound}}bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100{{/isTypeInbound}}">입고</button>
                    <button type="submit" name="type" value="OUTBOUND" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap {{#isTypeOutbound}}bg-slate-800 text-white{{/isTypeOutbound}}{{^isTypeOutbound}}bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100{{/isTypeOutbound}}">출고</button>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 w-full md:w-auto">
                    <div class="relative w-full md:w-64">
                        <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                        <input type="text" name="keyword" value="{{searchKeyword}}" placeholder="물품명 검색..." class="w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[800px]">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">일시</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">구분</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">물품명</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">수량</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">담당자</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">비고</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                        {{#histories}}
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">{{date}}</td>
                            <td class="p-4">
                                {{#isInbound}}
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-down-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i> 입고
                                </span>
                                {{/isInbound}}
                                {{#isOutbound}}
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-red-100 text-red-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i> 출고
                                </span>
                                {{/isOutbound}}
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">{{itemName}}</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                                {{#isInbound}}<span class="text-green-600">+{{quantity}}</span>{{/isInbound}}
                                {{#isOutbound}}<span class="text-red-600">-{{quantity}}</span>{{/isOutbound}}
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">{{managerName}}</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">{{memo}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        {{/histories}}

                        {{^histories}}
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="6" class="p-8 text-center text-slate-500">입출고 내역이 없습니다.</td>
                        </tr>
                        {{/histories}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-center">
                {{> partials/pagination}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>